{"tid":1668751,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[正視聽]任何叫人玩紙盒嘅都係支共帶風向","createTime":"2019-10-22T07:20:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-22T14:34:25.000Z","uid":183758,"like":12,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f830cf27955f7ddac3ba49d4e98b7b512c18a283","tid":1668751,"uid":183758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T07:20:24.000Z","msg":"典型中共套路<br />\n<br />\n想插贓嫁禍污名化人做恐怖分子<br />\n<br />\n喺度帶風向引你哋玩紙盒 之後就整個真嘅陷害你哋<br />\n<br />\n當年中共喺新疆都係用呢招<br />\n<br />\n就係想做出個觀感 因為你哋的確有放紙盒先 咁之後就算發生咩事都順利成章可以入曬你哋數<br />\n<br />\n連登大量支共mon po狗帶大風向 當中共無計可施就會用插贓嫁禍呢招  有撚曬前科用過唔止一次"},{"pid":"9894e66c0e89e21bbf98eb086675603953bfe8fa","tid":1668751,"uid":264529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T07:21:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"34db2f07352cc20d69537a6e0fdd49193e960948","tid":1668751,"uid":183758,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T07:25:43.000Z","msg":"佢就係想帶風向然之後做到先入為主的效果"},{"pid":"c2830be9be3e6277785b42716fb692a81558595b","tid":1668751,"uid":265168,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T07:32:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">快推行動po<br />\n推到有人搞</span></span><br />\n開咗兩個po都仲未上到熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n快啲一齊討論！<br />\n<br />\n[擴大戰線]  [行動] 與其嘈加泰集會 不如唔搞呢個<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1668190\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1668190</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5907da154139f2f49154e14c2c90db3f8942ae11","tid":1668751,"uid":51057,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T07:34:23.000Z","msg":"咪on9, 佢係要屈你既任何時候做d咩野都可以入你地數"},{"pid":"48f3c661a3e8a673304b9b73f2945215071da0ac","tid":1668751,"uid":183758,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5907da154139f2f49154e14c2c90db3f8942ae11","tid":1668751,"uid":51057,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T07:34:23.000Z","msg":"咪on9, 佢係要屈你既任何時候做d咩野都可以